{"tid":1963932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護朋友有福啦，林鄭為感謝醫護，豁免3年注冊費，護士230元","createTime":"2020-04-08T12:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T02:29:05.000Z","uid":23833,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5da5bdc821c8b9e0efbc3d3b48fcdba6879a5367","tid":1963932,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:42:19.000Z","msg":"]<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200408-13_NY6rl_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200408-13_NY6rl_1200x0.png&h=3eac2998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n特首林鄭月娥今日公布第二輪防疫抗疫基金的安排，當中包括豁免未來三年醫護人員註冊登記費，稱是為了肯定醫護的辛勞。<span style=\"color: red;\">根據護士管理局網頁，申請護士執業證明書的費用 230 元，有效期最長三年；而醫生執業駐冊費用每年 400 元。</span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又被追問會否承諾不向罷工醫護秋後算帳，林鄭僅稱這是醫管局與員工的問題，並不涉及特區政府。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭今日在記者會宣布，為了表達對醫護人員的感謝，在未來三年將豁免 12.5 萬名醫護人員註冊及登記費。有記者隨即指出，醫護人員從無要求減免開支，反問政府能否承諾不會對罷工醫護秋後算帳。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭回應稱，醫護人員的登記費金額不高，只是每年數百至千餘元，新措施是希望肯定醫護人員的辛勞，「但你提出的另一要求（承諾不秋後算帳）&hellip;這是醫管局作為僱主與員工的問題，並不涉及特區政府，因為我不是醫管局員工的僱主」。"},{"pid":"2b8eef4cd2ef9c232917d31bcbaa2ef3510a39a1","tid":1963932,"uid":321977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"嘩，食餐飯都無咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4570c3e3829c0bded067458955f7bbf3d5dcacdc","tid":1963932,"uid":22422,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:44:15.000Z","msg":"「但你提出的另一要求（承諾不秋後算帳）&hellip;這是醫管局作為僱主與員工的問題，並不涉及特區政府，因為我不是醫管局員工的僱主」。<br />\n<br />\n但係你條狗閪婆會對醫管局施壓嘛<br />\n賤格老閪殼"},{"pid":"bc4b42e19c8e0e531f6caa133e02800218255873","tid":1963932,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5831e135d3e3867cb3efcd8de58fd08859c141","tid":1963932,"uid":321330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:45:54.000Z","msg":"德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 加佢0.1分"},{"pid":"a1d4ee6bb630ac55cc8831b942055f5f48a1b041","tid":1963932,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:56:33.000Z","msg":"$230 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9adf734a2618dd46ec73ef5532fab479bd0f0656","tid":1963932,"uid":130177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"好好啦 其他打工仔一蚊都無"},{"pid":"ab01862a913197567187f6afff930156c534595f","tid":1963932,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1d4ee6bb630ac55cc8831b942055f5f48a1b041","tid":1963932,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:56:33.000Z","msg":"$230 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:02:10.000Z","msg":"唔夠買盒好少少既口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60e432b6f321daa2a2fd739d153b40bd4e54ea0a","tid":1963932,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:03:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>佢比乞兒都比500啦屌你老母</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"51bb14041110c73bd0e5e1828058e07e1d4ed3fb","tid":1963932,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:05:28.000Z","msg":"疫情過左肯定搞9醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805fdb05064715fd377a37edcacb398ea910f632","tid":1963932,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T01:59:51.000Z","msg":"點解無醫護屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b0ded6bf3229305150611bb1cba241dab03584","tid":1